<div class="gothic-tales gt-dialog gt-herbalism-player">
  <header class="gt-profession-tools-header">
    <div>
      <div class="gt-talent-chat-kicker">Berufs-Minispiel</div>
      <h2><i class="fas fa-seedling"></i> Kräuterkunde</h2>
      <p>Kraut wählen, suchen und Fund automatisch ins Inventar übernehmen.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  {{#if note}}
  <div class="gt-help-box">{{note}}</div>
  {{/if}}

  {{#if blocked}}
  <div class="gt-help-box gt-warning-box">{{blockedReason}}</div>
  {{/if}}

  <div class="gt-state-grid">
    <div><span>Grad</span><strong>{{rank.label}}</strong></div>
    <div><span>Suchen</span><strong>{{successes}} / {{maxSearches}}</strong></div>
    <div><span>Verbleibend</span><strong>{{remaining}}</strong></div>
    <div><span>Timer</span><strong>{{cooldownText}}</strong></div>
    <div><span>Ort</span><strong>{{#if outdoors}}freie Natur{{else}}ungeeignet{{/if}}</strong></div>
    <div><span>Unterstützung</span><strong>nicht möglich</strong></div>
  </div>

  <label>Kraut wählen
    <select class="gt-herbalism-herb">
      {{#each herbs}}<option value="{{id}}" {{#if selected}}selected{{/if}}>{{label}} · SchwG {{difficulty}} · {{use}} · Wert {{valueText}}</option>{{/each}}
    </select>
  </label>

  <div class="gt-herb-detail">
    <h3>{{selectedHerb.label}}</h3>
    <p>SchwG <strong>{{selectedHerb.difficulty}}</strong> · Nutzung: <strong>{{selectedHerb.use}}</strong> · Wert: <strong>{{selectedHerb.value}}</strong></p>
    <p>Bei Heil- und Manakräutern entspricht die Menge dem Wurfergebnis. Bei kritischem Erfolg gibt es zusätzlich Kronstöckel.</p>
  </div>

  <footer class="gt-dialog-actions">
    <button type="button" class="gt-herbalism-search" {{#if blocked}}disabled{{/if}}><i class="fas fa-dice-d20"></i> Kraut suchen</button>
    {{#if isGM}}
    <button type="button" class="gt-herbalism-reset-timer"><i class="fas fa-hourglass-start"></i> Timer zurücksetzen</button>
    <button type="button" class="gt-herbalism-reset-session"><i class="fas fa-rotate-left"></i> Sitzung zurücksetzen</button>
    {{/if}}
    <button type="button" class="gt-dialog-cancel"><i class="fas fa-xmark"></i> Schließen</button>
  </footer>
</div>
